text: Kouk Thlok Commune () is a khum (commune) in Angkor Borei District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, the commune has 4 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21010301 |Prek Ta Pha (Preaek Ta Pha) |ព្រែកតាផ |- !2 |21010302 |Prek Da (Preaek Da) |ព្រែកដា |- !3 |21010303 |Tuol Puttrea |ទួលពុទ្រា |- !4 |21010304 |Bak Dai |បាក់ដៃ |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Angkor Borei District
